headline: Government & Technical Consulting Stocks Q2 Teardown: Jacobs Solutions (NYSE:J) Vs The Rest
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Jacobs Solutions (NYSE:J) and the best and worst performers in the government & technical consulting industry.
